name: Rocket Boost (Ducaluk)
description:
The solar system is messed up. Can you find your way back to home?

Go from the blue platform to the green to finish a level. Make sure to not spin out of control or a fiery explosion awaits you.

Please play in full screen for best mode to play in.

Note this is a game based on a learning tutorial. https://www.udemy.com/course/unitycourse2/
